==English==
===Etymology===
Spelling out of NZ, the abbreviation of [[New Zealand]], + [[-er]], denoting a native of a place.

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛdə(r)|-ɛdə(r)]]

===Proper noun===
'''Enzedder''' (''plural'' '''Enzedders''')

# {{colloquial}} A [[New Zealander]].

